Text.string: Hello, Vault Hunter!
It is good to see you!
Always good to see a friendly face!
Vault Hunter! Thank the storms you've come.
The storms have brought you to me.
Perhaps nonviolence isn't the proper response to such aggression.
If only we were allowed to raise arms against our oppressors.
I must not question the teachings.
Hither and yon we scurry, questioning our small lot in life.
I'll admit I'm intrigued by the violent ways of our saviors.
Yours is the path of righteous violence. Mine is the path of righteous pacifism.
I almost envy your blood-drenched pursuit of justice.
Woe to any who stand against you, Vault Hunter!
We were properly doomed until you came along!
Were I a fighting man, I would join you in your quest.
Farewell, Vault Hunter!
Until next time, my friend!
May the wind be ever at your back.
Let the storms guide you!
Listen, and the storms shall lead the way.
